<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span>٢٤ - باب<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span>الموقف<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span><span style="color:#006d98">من الصحاح:</span><a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span>٢٧٢ - ٧٩٠ -<span style="color:#006d98"> وقال جابر رضي الله عنه:</span> قام رسول الله صلى الله عليه وسلم ليصلي ,<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>